item.title: How Do Cats Always Land on Their Feet?🐈‍⬛😼 The Science Explained!
item.dc:creator: Soham Mahajan
item.description: Cats are famous for their ability to always land on their feet, but how do they pull off this incredible feat? Discover the fascinating science and reflexes behind a cat’s righting ability and learn why they are nature’s acrobats.
